      <title>尼日利亚奈拉跌至新低，因央行撤回支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/nigerian-naira-at-fresh-low-as-central-bank-dials-back-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚奈拉兑美元汇率跌至新低，分析师将此归咎于流动性不足，因为央行减少了干预，而外国投资者则从国内债券中获利了结。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/nigerian-naira-at-fresh-low-as-central-bank-dials-back-support</guid>
